These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, rugby, basketball
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, backgammon, monopoly
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, ship, subway, van
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the van is between the person playing snooker and the person who's sport is baseball##2
3. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person playing chess is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Sport   | baseball    | rugby      | cycling      | basketball    |
| Game   | monopoly | chess | snooker | backgammon |
| Transport     | ship    | van       | subway     | bus     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, boat, scooter, skateboard
City: berlin, hamburg, hannover, liverpool
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, romance, superhero, thriller
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Transport          | quad-bike     | skateboard     | boat       | scooter    |
| City         | hamburg | hannover   | berlin | liverpool |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | superhero | romance    | epic        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, disco, gospel, country
There are 4 different nationalities: british, dutch, malaysian, polish
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, garlic, pomegranate, banana
1. the dutch is on the far right##1
2. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the british##3
4. the fan of blues is on the left of the person eating banana##1
5. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the fan of country is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the fan of blues is on the far left##1
8. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre      | blues | disco  | gospel    | country |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | polish  | british  | dutch    |
| Food         | garlic    | banana | pumpkin | pomegranate  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, brazilian, turkish, german
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, family, time-travel
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, magic-tricks, sudoku, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person watching drama movies and the egyptian##2
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the turkish##1
4. the turkish is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the german##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
7. the german is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the brazilian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality          | turkish   | egyptian     | brazilian | german |
| Movie-Genre   | family | time-travel | action   | drama     |
| Hobby           | fishing | sudoku      | magic-tricks     | rock-climbing       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
City: hannover, berlin, new-york, san-francisco
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, lawyer, librarian
4 different games are played: canasta, domino, mah-jongg, poker
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
3. the lawyer is the person playing canasta##1
4. the architect is between the person traveling to new-york and the person traveling to berlin##2
5. the lawyer is on the right of the librarian##1
6. the person playing domino is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
7. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
8. the person traveling to new-york is the person playing mah-jongg##1
9. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| City          | new-york      | san-francisco | berlin      | hannover |
| Job           | dressmaker | architect | librarian | lawyer   |
| Game   | mah-jongg    | poker   | domino     | canasta   |

