.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, entrepreneur, videographer
City: liverpool, prague, paris, miami
4 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, poker, canasta
1. the person playing snooker is the coach##1
2. the person playing poker is the person traveling to miami##1
3. the coach is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
5. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
6. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
7. the doctor is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
8. the doctor is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | coach    | doctor   | entrepreneur | videographer |
| City   | liverpool     | paris   | miami         | prague        |
| Game         | snooker | monopoly | poker         | canasta       |

