.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
4 different games are played: whist, go, mah-jongg, poker
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, doctor, videographer
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, azure, purple, apricot
 1. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
 2. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 3. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
 4. the doctor is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 5. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person playing go##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 7. the doctor is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 8. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 9. the person who likes white is on the right of the person playing go##1
10. the dancer is on the left or right of the doctor##3
11. the dancer is the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Game         | mah-jongg    | whist  | go | poker   |
| Job           | videographer | dancer   | doctor    | bartender |
| Color   | apricot      | purple | azure | white  |

