.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, pineapple, watermelon, zucchini
House: tower, craftsman, colonial, modern
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rat, turtle, guinea-pig
1. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
4. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
6. the craftsman house is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the modern house is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
8. the colonial house is on the left or right of the modern house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pineapple    | zucchini | broccoli    |
| House         | colonial     | modern | craftsman  | tower |
| Pet   | rat    | guinea-pig      | chinchilla   | turtle         |

