.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, tea, water
House: cottage, modern, colonial, townhouse
City: rome, boston, colone, edinburgh
1. the modern house is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the cottage house##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
4. the colonial house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
7. the townhouse house is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | tea            | water     | fanta      |
| House           | cottage    | townhouse | colonial     | modern |
| City   | rome | colone    | boston | edinburgh    |

