The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, horror, thriller
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, train, tram, bike
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the journalist##1
3. the scientist is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
4. the project-manager is on the far right##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is the project-manager##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the videographer##1
7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
8. the scientist is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Job          | scientist   | journalist | videographer | project-manager |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | crime     | action      | thriller  |
| Transport   | van | train   | tram    | bike   |

