.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-11::.
City: liverpool, venice, colone, new-york
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, drama, scientific
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, bike, roller, scooter
1. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
7. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person driving the car##1
8. the person driving the car is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
| City           | new-york | venice        | liverpool   | colone  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy             | animation     | scientific | drama  |
| Transport         | bike           | scooter | car   | roller |

