.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, soy-milk, sprite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, romance, scientific, animation
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, chestnut, ebony, ivory
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
6. the person who likes ivory is between the person who likes chestnut and the person drinking mirinda##2
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person watching romance movies##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk   | mirinda    | sprite |
| Movie-Genre         | romance | scientific    | action      | animation |
| Color   | chestnut      | ivory | ebony | black   |

