.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea, milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, musical, drama, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, d&b, blues, house
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of soul##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is between the person drinking coffee and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person watching musical movies is the fan of house##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
6. the person drinking coffee is the person watching drama movies##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
8. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the fan of blues is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | coffee      | almond-milk | milk       | iced-tea  |
| Movie-Genre       | drama | adventure | mystery    | musical |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | soul         | blues | house     |

