3. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating cherry is the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the person eating raspberry is between the person eating cherry and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
7. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
