The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, tennis, climbing, biathlon
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rat, snake, turtle
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
4. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
7. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
8. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |      3       |     4      |
| Hobby           | camping | board-games | fishing | dancing      |
| Sport   | climbing   | biathlon | tennis       | rugby  |
| Pet           | rat          | snake  | turtle       | guinea-pig |

