.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, juice, lemonade
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, daffodil, dahlia, balloon-flower
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, davidoff, fonseca, baccarat
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking coffee is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is between the aristoff-smoker and the fonseca-smoker##2
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
8. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| Beverage    | juice   | lemonade    | coffee      | almond-milk |
| Flower       | daisy  | daffodil | balloon-flower | dahlia     |
| Cigar   | aristoff | davidoff        | fonseca  | baccarat        |

