.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, sprite, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, jazz, disco, classical
There 4 different types of food: corn, spinach, grapefruit, apricot
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of classical##1
2. the person drinking sprite is between the fan of classical and the person eating grapefruit##2
3. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
4. the fan of r&b is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking sprite is between the person eating apricot and the person drinking water##2
6. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
7. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Beverage      | water      | sprite     | juice | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | jazz    | classical   | r&b |
| Food     | grapefruit | spinach | apricot   | corn    |

