.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-19::.
House: cottage, townhouse, art-deco, cape-cod
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, kale, kiwi, mango
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, magic-tricks, collecting, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
3. the cottage house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
6. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the townhouse house is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
8. the person eating asparagus is between the townhouse house and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| House      | townhouse | cape-cod    | cottage | art-deco  |
| Food          | kale          | asparagus | mango       | kiwi      |
| Hobby   | collecting     | magic-tricks    | woodworking     | baking |

