The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, journalist, security-guard
4 different games are played: chess, whist, billiard, poker
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
2. the person playing whist is on the right of the bartender##1
3. the person playing billiard is the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
5. the person playing whist is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growsorchid##2
6. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
7. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
8. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Flower    | orchid | sunflower  | marigold  | dahlia           |
| Job     | bartender | journalist | dancer   | security-guard |
| Game   | poker   | whist       | chess | billiard  |

 